---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
const lastUpdated = "July 21, 2026";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"
    />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Read the Runi Designs Privacy Policy and learn how information submitted through our website is collected, used, stored, and protected."
    />

    <title>Privacy Policy | Runi Designs</title>
    <link
      rel="icon"
      type="image/svg+xml"
      href="/images/runi-mark.svg"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="policy-header">
      <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Return to Runi Designs homepage">
        <span class="brand-mark">
          <img src="/images/runi-mark.svg" alt="" />
        </span>

        <span>Runi Designs</span>
      </a>

      <a class="return-link" href="/">
        Return to website
        <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="policy-hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">Legal & privacy</p>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p class="hero-description">
          This policy explains what information Runi Designs collects through
          this website and how that information is used, stored, and protected.
        </p>

        <p class="updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </section>

      <div class="policy-layout">
        <aside class="policy-navigation">
          <p>On this page</p>

          <nav aria-label="Privacy policy sections">
            <a href="#information">Information we collect</a>
            <a href="#use">How we use information</a>
            <a href="#files">Uploaded artwork</a>
            <a href="#sharing">How information is shared</a>
            <a href="#retention">Data retention</a>
            <a href="#security">Data security</a>
            <a href="#choices">Your choices</a>
            <a href="#children">Children’s privacy</a>
            <a href="#changes">Policy updates</a>
            <a href="#contact">Contact us</a>
          </nav>
        </aside>

        <article class="policy-content">
          <section id="introduction">
            <h2>Our commitment</h2>

            <p>
              Runi Designs respects your privacy. We collect only the
              information reasonably needed to respond to inquiries, prepare
              custom quotes, create designs, fulfill orders, communicate with
              customers, and operate this website.
            </p>

            <p>
              By using this website or submitting information through the
              quote-request form, you acknowledge the practices described in
              this Privacy Policy.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="information">
            <p class="section-number">01</p>
            <h2>Information we collect</h2>

            <p>
              When you submit a quote request, we may collect information you
              provide, including:
            </p>

            <ul>
              <li>Your name</li>
              <li>Your email address</li>
              <li>Your phone number</li>
              <li>The product you are interested in</li>
              <li>Your requested quantity and needed-by date</li>
              <li>Project descriptions, preferences, and other details</li>
              <li>Logos, artwork, photographs, PDFs, or other uploaded files</li>
            </ul>

            <p>
              Our website and hosting providers may also process limited
              technical information needed to deliver, protect, and troubleshoot
              the website, such as an IP address, browser type, device type,
              request time, and security-related logs.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="use">
            <p class="section-number">02</p>
            <h2>How we use information</h2>

            <p>We may use the information we collect to:</p>

            <ul>
              <li>Review and respond to quote requests</li>
              <li>Contact you about your project</li>
              <li>Prepare pricing, designs, proofs, and mockups</li>
              <li>Determine product and deadline availability</li>
              <li>Create and fulfill approved orders</li>
              <li>Provide customer support</li>
              <li>Protect the website from spam, misuse, or security threats</li>
              <li>Maintain business, tax, transaction, and project records</li>
              <li>Comply with applicable legal obligations</li>
            </ul>

            <p>
              We do not sell or rent personal information submitted through
              this website.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="files">
            <p class="section-number">03</p>
            <h2>Uploaded logos and artwork</h2>

            <p>
              Files uploaded through the quote form are used to evaluate,
              prepare, design, produce, or discuss your requested product.
              Uploaded files are stored in private cloud storage and are not
              intentionally made available to the public.
            </p>

            <p>
              Please upload only files you own or are authorized to use. Avoid
              submitting sensitive personal information that is not necessary
              for your project.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="sharing">
            <p class="section-number">04</p>
            <h2>How information is shared</h2>

            <p>
              We may share or allow access to information only when reasonably
              necessary for business operations, including with:
            </p>

            <ul>
              <li>
                Website hosting, storage, email, security, and technology
                service providers
              </li>
              <li>
                Vendors or production partners assisting with an approved order
              </li>
              <li>
                Professional advisers such as accountants or legal advisers
              </li>
              <li>
                Government authorities when disclosure is legally required
              </li>
            </ul>

            <p>
              Service providers may process information only as needed to
              provide their services or meet applicable legal obligations.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="retention">
            <p class="section-number">05</p>
            <h2>Data retention</h2>

            <p>
              Quote requests, communications, uploaded files, designs, and
              order records are retained only for as long as reasonably needed
              to respond to your request, complete the project, maintain
              business records, resolve disputes, prevent fraud, or comply with
              legal and accounting requirements.
            </p>

            <p>
              Information that is no longer reasonably needed may be deleted,
              anonymized, or securely disposed of.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="security">
            <p class="section-number">06</p>
            <h2>Data security</h2>

            <p>
              We use reasonable administrative and technical safeguards
              designed to protect information against unauthorized access,
              alteration, disclosure, loss, or misuse.
            </p>

            <p>
              Quote information and uploaded files are stored through
              Cloudflare services. However, no website, transmission method, or
              storage system can be guaranteed to be completely secure.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="choices">
            <p class="section-number">07</p>
            <h2>Your choices and requests</h2>

            <p>
              You may contact us to request access to, correction of, or
              deletion of personal information you previously submitted.
              Certain information may need to be retained for legitimate
              business, transaction, tax, security, or legal purposes.
            </p>

            <p>
              To make a privacy request, email
              <a href="mailto:runidesigns@outlook.com">
                runidesigns@outlook.com
              </a>.
              We may ask for information needed to verify the request.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="children">
            <p class="section-number">08</p>
            <h2>Children’s privacy</h2>

            <p>
              This website is intended for customers seeking custom products
              and is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly
              collect personal information from children under 13 through the
              website.
            </p>

            <p>
              If you believe a child submitted personal information, contact us
              so we can review and, where appropriate, delete it.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="links">
            <p class="section-number">09</p>
            <h2>Third-party websites</h2>

            <p>
              This website may eventually contain links to social media
              platforms or other third-party websites. Their privacy practices
              are controlled by their own policies, not this Privacy Policy.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="changes">
            <p class="section-number">10</p>
            <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>

            <p>
              We may update this Privacy Policy when our website, services,
              technology, or legal obligations change. The updated version will
              be posted on this page with a revised “Last updated” date.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section id="contact">
            <p class="section-number">11</p>
            <h2>Contact us</h2>

            <p>
              Questions or requests regarding this Privacy Policy may be sent
              to:
            </p>

            <div class="contact-card">
              <p><strong>Runi Designs</strong></p>

              <a href="mailto:runidesigns@outlook.com">
                runidesigns@outlook.com
              </a>

              <p>Columbus, Ohio, United States</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <div class="policy-disclaimer">
            <p>
              This policy is intended to describe the current website
              practices of Runi Designs. It does not create contractual rights
              beyond those required by applicable law.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>© {currentYear} Runi Designs. All rights reserved.</p>

      <div>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <style>
      :root {
        font-family:
          Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        color: #f7f7f5;
        background: #080808;
        font-synthesis: none;
        text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        min-width: 320px;
        min-height: 100vh;
        background:
          radial-gradient(
            circle at 75% 10%,
            rgb(197 167 123 / 12%),
            transparent 25%
          ),
          #080808;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      section {
        scroll-margin-top: 110px;
      }

      .policy-header {
        position: fixed;
        z-index: 100;
        top: 16px;
        left: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        width: min(calc(100% - 32px), 1320px);
        padding: 12px 14px 12px 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgb(255 255 255 / 12%);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgb(12 12 12 / 75%);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 50px rgb(0 0 0 / 25%);
        backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(140%);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(140%);
        transform: translateX(-50%);
      }

      .brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 650;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      .brand-mark {
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid rgb(255 255 255 / 18%);
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: rgb(255 255 255 / 7%);
      }

      .brand-mark img {
        display: block;
        width: 26px;
        height: 26px;
        object-fit: contain;
      }

      .return-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 12px 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #f4f1eb;
        color: #111111;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        transition:
          gap 180ms ease,
          transform 180ms ease;
      }

      .return-link:hover {
        gap: 14px;
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }

      .policy-hero {
        max-width: 1320px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 190px clamp(24px, 7vw, 80px) 110px;
      }

      .eyebrow,
      .section-number {
        color: #c5a77b;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.17em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h1 {
        max-width: 960px;
        margin-top: 24px;
        font-size: clamp(64px, 10vw, 142px);
        font-weight: 560;
        line-height: 0.9;
        letter-spacing: -0.075em;
      }

      .hero-description {
        max-width: 710px;
        margin-top: 35px;
        color: rgb(255 255 255 / 58%);
        font-size: clamp(18px, 1.7vw, 22px);
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .updated {
        margin-top: 28px;
        color: rgb(255 255 255 / 34%);
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      .policy-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 250px minmax(0, 800px);
        justify-content: center;
        gap: clamp(60px, 9vw, 140px);
        padding: 40px clamp(24px, 7vw, 110px) 150px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgb(255 255 255 / 8%);
      }

      .policy-navigation {
        position: sticky;
        top: 130px;
        align-self: start;
        padding-top: 14px;
      }

      .policy-navigation > p {
        margin-bottom: 22px;
        color: rgb(255 255 255 / 32%);
        font-size: 11px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .policy-navigation nav {
        display: grid;
        gap: 4px;
      }

      .policy-navigation a {
        padding: 10px 12px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        color: rgb(255 255 255 / 45%);
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.4;
        transition:
          color 180ms ease,
          background 180ms ease;
      }

      .policy-navigation a:hover {
        background: rgb(255 255 255 / 6%);
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .policy-content {
        min-width: 0;
      }

      .policy-content section {
        padding: 70px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(255 255 255 / 9%);
      }

      .policy-content section:first-child {
        padding-top: 0;
      }

      .policy-content h2 {
        margin-top: 14px;
        font-size: clamp(34px, 4vw, 52px);
        font-weight: 560;
        line-height: 1;
        letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      }

      .policy-content p,
      .policy-content li {
        color: rgb(255 255 255 / 58%);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.85;
      }

      .policy-content h2 + p,
      .policy-content p + p,
      .policy-content p + ul,
      .policy-content ul + p {
        margin-top: 24px;
      }

      .policy-content ul {
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-left: 22px;
      }

      .policy-content a {
        color: #e2c595;
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-decoration-color: rgb(226 197 149 / 35%);
        text-underline-offset: 5px;
      }

      .contact-card {
        display: grid;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-top: 26px;
        padding: 28px;
        border: 1px solid rgb(255 255 255 / 10%);
        border-radius: 22px;
        background: rgb(255 255 255 / 4%);
      }

      .contact-card p,
      .contact-card a {
        margin: 0;
      }

      .policy-disclaimer {
        margin-top: 45px;
        padding: 24px;
        border: 1px solid rgb(197 167 123 / 18%);
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgb(197 167 123 / 6%);
      }

      .policy-disclaimer p {
        color: rgb(255 255 255 / 43%);
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      footer {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 30px;
        padding: 30px clamp(24px, 7vw, 110px);
        border-top: 1px solid rgb(255 255 255 / 9%);
        color: rgb(255 255 255 / 34%);
        font-size: 12px;
      }

      footer div {
        display: flex;
        gap: 22px;
      }

      footer a:hover {
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .policy-layout {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .policy-navigation {
          display: none;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 560px) {
        .policy-header {
          top: 10px;
          width: calc(100% - 20px);
          padding: 10px 10px 10px 14px;
        }

        .brand {
          font-size: 14px;
        }

        .brand-mark {
          width: 36px;
          height: 36px;
        }

        .return-link {
          padding: 10px 13px;
          font-size: 11px;
        }

        .return-link span {
          display: none;
        }

        .policy-hero {
          padding: 155px 20px 80px;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: clamp(58px, 19vw, 88px);
        }

        .policy-layout {
          padding: 10px 20px 100px;
        }

        .policy-content section {
          padding: 55px 0;
        }

        .policy-content p,
        .policy-content li {
          font-size: 15px;
        }

        footer {
          align-items: flex-start;
          flex-direction: column;
          padding: 28px 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>